messages: RUSSIA: Sorry I didn't have time to get to you.. Austria and Italy sent me a lot of messages last turn

RUSSIA: Why did you go to Armenia? I agree I would like to divide up the Balkans with a good ally, but now your fleet is off in the corner in a bad spot. If you move it back to Ank I think we will have a better path to working together against Austria and Italy
TURKEY: It's definitely been busy!
TURKEY: I don't like endless squabbles over Bla. We can decide to move forward at this point together, when everyone thinks that you have the upper hand
RUSSIA: Ok, will you go back to Ankara or do I have to guess over whether to bounce you in Sev or block Black Sea?

messages: TURKEY: I guess all that remains is for me to make sure you don't get any territory.

RUSSIA: Austria and Italy are going to become really powerful now and I need allies. If you stop throwing yourself at me for no reason, and instead defend your centers, we can rekindle something
TURKEY: I honestly don't mind! :)
